Title: Mousou Teikoku Chikuonki
Description: ['Music video directed by Kousuke Sugimoto for the single ', Mousou Teikoku Chikuonki, ' by Eri Kitamura. The limited edition version included a DVD with this music video, a making-of, and a short version that was released on the Teichiku Records YouTube channel in December of 2017 to promote the single.']
